CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Jeffs Brands Ltd is an e-commerce CPG company, operating primarily on Amazon. The company serves as the holding company of three other e-commerce companies, Smart Repair Pro, Purex, and Top Rank, that operate online stores for the sale of various consumer products on Amazon online marketplace, utilizing the FBA model. The company has five wholly-owned subsidiaries: Smart Repair Pro, Purex, Top Rank , Fort and Jeffs' Brands Holdings.
